    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs like a dream, and is honestly just waiting for its next adventure. Whether you\u2019re planning a road trip or just need a dependable daily driver, this one won't let you down. The interior is nice and clean, and it's totally ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I\u2019d love to help you get behind the wheel!",
