    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a 2018 BMW 540i finished in sophisticated Glacier Silver Metallic with a premium Black Dakota Leather interior. This vehicle has been driven with care and serves as an excellent example of a well-maintained luxury sedan. The exterior bodywork is straight and clean, showing only light, age-appropriate wear such as minor stone chips on the lower front valance. The paint maintains a high-gloss finish and has been regularly waxed. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather seats are firm and free of cracks or stains, and the genuine wood trim remains unblemished. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system, heads-up display, and multi-zone climate control, are in full working order. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine runs smoothly, supported by a comprehensive service history performed at BMW-certified centers. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Continental run-flat tires with ample tread. This car comes with two keys, the original owner's manuals, and a clean title. It is a reliable, high-performance machine ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated driver. It exhibits a refined exterior finish and a well-preserved interior, reflecting a consistent standard of care. Our rigorous inspection process confirms that all mechanical systems operate with precision and reliability. This offering combines robust performance with distinguished styling, ensuring a superior driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
